0.8.0
  rts2-centrald  Logic for detecting missing devices.

  Mailing

  sendMailMessage

  RTS2 scripting

  C, HEX commands needs for proper functionality name of the device  

  rts2-xmlrpcclient

  It is now possible to set RTS2 variable by XML-RPC call. Either use some
  custom XML-RPC library and call rts2.values.set with device, var and value
  filled in (look to src/xmlrpc/xmlrpcclient.cpp for an example) or use
  rts2-xmlrpcclient with -s option (see rts2-xmlrpcclient for small help).

  rts2-image
  
  -l option to create softlinks

  rts2-sensor-pixy (lightening sensor)

  rts2-sensor-mrakomer (cloud sensor)

  rts2-user binary (see man rts2-user for details)

  -N option (do not pretty print) for rts2-nightreport, rts2-target, rts2-targetlist, rts2-targetinfo and rts2-telmodeltest

  rts2-logd check for expansion pattern changes

  Scheduler support - uses new tables "tickets", "accounts", etc..
